title: OCE | SLaTerStream is live come see me grind to gold

embed.description: OCE | Welcome to SLaTerStream | Doing my Promo's | Platinum Here I Come!

body:
Hey guys I am a new streamer from WA. Got placed into Silver 1 yesterday and that just isn't good enough so come watch me grind my way up tp gold again.
I'm always watching chat so come share your thoughts even if it's to say I should probably be in Wood league :)

SLaTerStream
